<lyrics>[V1]
 1- nbạrk ạsmk fy kl ywm .. wtsbyḥạtnạ ạ̉frạḥ tdwm
 kl ạlmsyrẗ ḥr wgẖywm .. htạf bʿzẗ yạ rb lyk
 ạlqrạr- snyn tʿdy wfy kl lḥẓẗ .. bndrk ạ̹nk ạ̹lh ạ̉myn
 sạʿdnạ nsẖkr nfrḥ wnṭlb .. srʿẗ mjyỷk tʿạl ạ̉myn
 tfḍl gẖạytnạ whdf ḥạytnạ .. fy trnymạtnạ ṭwl ạlsnyn
 nʿysẖ nmjd nsẖhd wnʿln .. tkrys qlwbnạ yạ rb lyk
 tkrys qlwbnạ (yạ rb lyk)2
 2- ʿạysẖyn fy ḍlk mn gẖyr ạ̉nyn .. bạytyn fy strk wfrḥạnyn
 wạtẖqyn fy wʿdk ạ̹nt ạlạ̉myn .. ạ̹nk ḥạfẓnạ yạ rb lyk
 3- ḥbk mạlynạ fy lyl ṭwyl .. dạ ạnt ạlly lynạ rb wkẖlyl
 wjhk hạdynạ bnwr jmyl .. nwṣl dyạrnạ yạ rb lyk</lyrics>
<title>nbạrk ạsmk fy kl ywm</title>
